# Multi-Sport Venue Reservation — Database Schema

Build the complete database layer for a venue reservation platform that supports **multiple sports** (padel, tennis, badminton, futsal, etc.), not just padel.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Sport-agnostic design**: The schema uses a `sports` table so venues and courts can be tagged with any sport type. The app name is "VibePadel" but the data model is flexible.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Pricing model**: The plan stores price **per court** (each court has its own hourly rate). If you prefer venue-level or time-based dynamic pricing (e.g. peak hours cost more), let me know.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Booking flow**: A booking ties one user → one court → one date + time range. Multi-slot bookings are a single row with `start_time` / `end_time` (not multiple rows). If you want to support booking multiple courts at once, let me know.

---

## Entity Relationship Diagram

```mermaid
erDiagram
    USERS ||--o{ BOOKINGS : "makes"
    USERS ||--o{ REVIEWS : "writes"
    SPORTS ||--o{ COURTS : "played on"
    VENUES ||--o{ COURTS : "has"
    VENUES ||--o{ REVIEWS : "receives"
    VENUES }o--o{ VENUE_FACILITIES : "has"
    FACILITIES ||--o{ VENUE_FACILITIES : "belongs to"
    COURTS ||--o{ BOOKINGS : "reserved via"
    BOOKINGS ||--o| PAYMENTS : "paid by"

    SPORTS {
        id bigint PK
        name string
        slug string UK
        icon string
    }

    VENUES {
        id bigint PK
        name string
        slug string UK
        description text
        address string
        city string
        latitude decimal
        longitude decimal
        phone string
        image_url string
        is_active boolean
    }

    FACILITIES {
        id bigint PK
        name string
        icon string
    }

    VENUE_FACILITIES {
        venue_id bigint FK
        facility_id bigint FK
    }

    COURTS {
        id bigint PK
        venue_id bigint FK
        sport_id bigint FK
        name string
        type enum
        price_per_hour integer
        is_active boolean
    }

    BOOKINGS {
        id bigint PK
        user_id bigint FK
        court_id bigint FK
        date date
        start_time time
        end_time time
        total_price integer
        status enum
        notes text
    }

    PAYMENTS {
        id bigint PK
        booking_id bigint FK
        method enum
        amount integer
        status enum
        paid_at timestamp
    }

    REVIEWS {
        id bigint PK
        user_id bigint FK
        venue_id bigint FK
        rating tinyint
        comment text
    }
```

