## Proposed Changes

### Migrations (7 new files)

All prices are stored as **integers in Rupiah** (no decimals needed for IDR).

#### [NEW] `create_sports_table.php`
| Column | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `id` | bigint | PK |
| `name` | string | e.g. "Padel", "Tenis", "Badminton" |
| `slug` | string | unique, URL-friendly |
| `icon` | string, nullable | Icon name or emoji |
| timestamps | | |

